This Kettering Authentication Service (KAS) allows you to access your Kettering University web services. KAS is one set of credentials allowing you to access any of your web services for a set number of hours, without having to login again.
By logging in via KAS, you agree to abide by the University’s
Security warning for shared use computers:
The only reliable way to sign out of KAS or other web applications is to exit your web browser.
Log out of any shared computer before you leave it.
Log out of any and all web applications, do not just close your web browser
Do not save your password in any web browser
Log out of or lock the computer before you leave it
